}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The third receive chain has been omitted.
If there are [http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?p=620603 multiple revisions of the device], I don't know what the differences between revisions are (if any). The RAM and flash amount are assumed to be 4 and 16MB as specified in that post.
"1244-00000548-01Z" may be silkscreened on the board.
The FCC test report lists the following as identical models.. *Edimax EW-7416-APn / GAP-416n *Hawking HWABN1 / HWREN1 *Sitecom WL-330
